44-4716.Agents.

No individual may apply, procure, negotiate, or place for others any policy or contract of a prepaid limited health service organization unless that individual holds a license pursuant to the Insurance Producers Licensing Act to sell accident and health insurance policies or health maintenance organization contracts.

SourceLaws 1989, LB 320, ยง 16.

Cross ReferencesInsurance Producers Licensing Act, see section 44-4047.
